@node L13 "1.3 Improvements over v2.00"

                          Improvements over v2.00

The main improvements are:

1. Bugs squished, most minor, one major!

2. The Gobbledir utility added

3. The ability to convert subdirectories added

4. DOS character conversion added, with better interface

